SECTION 1: DEFINITIONS
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

"Licensed Material" means the specifications, protocols, synthesis procedures,
characterization methods, theoretical documents, certainty briefs, and all
associated materials in this repository.

"Non-Commercial Use" means use that is not primarily intended for or directed
toward commercial advantage or monetary compensation. This includes:
  - Academic research and publication
  - Educational use at any level
  - Personal study and experimentation
  - Verification attempts by any qualified party
  - Non-profit humanitarian manufacture and distribution
  - Government research programs
  - Open science contributions

"Commercial Use" means any use primarily intended for or directed toward
commercial advantage or monetary compensation. This includes:
  - Commercial manufacture of materials or products
  - Commercial sale or distribution
  - Commercial clinical trials or regulatory submissions
  - Licensing to third parties for commercial purposes
  - Use in commercial products or services
  - Any application generating revenue from the Licensed Material

"Licensor" means Universal Standard Axiom Corporation, represented by
Michael A. Russell, Michael@advanceerivs.com.

